  "conclusion": {
    "zh": "XGBoost（历史销量+车型配置+舆情特征）在 150 系评估集上取得最低体积加权 WMAPE。特征重要性由销量自身滞后（上月销量、近三月均值）绝对主导，即历史惯性驱动预测；舆情等外生特征在月粒度预测中增益有限——其价值在销量归因环节得到验证（见归因屏）。",
    "en": "XGBoost (historical sales + vehicle config + sentiment) achieves the lowest volume-weighted WMAPE on the 150-series set. Feature importance is dominated by sales lag features (previous month, 3-month average) — historical momentum drives the forecast; exogenous features like sentiment add little at monthly granularity, and their value is validated in the attribution step (see Attribution)."
  },
  "best_model": "XGBoost",
  "feature_insight": {
    "zh": "前两位都是销量自身滞后/移动平均，说明预测主要依赖「惯性」；能源类型、车辆级别等配置属性提供车型截面差异；舆情特征（正/负面占比、智能化滞后）排在末尾，提示动态口碑不是强预测信号。",
    "en": "The top two features are sales lags/moving averages, confirming the forecast relies mostly on momentum. Energy type and vehicle class provide cross-sectional differences. Sentiment features (positive/negative ratios, intelligence lag) rank low, suggesting dynamic word-of-mouth is not a strong predictor."
  }
}